  <brief_title>To Investigate the Effect of Early Community-care Program on Fracture Hip Patient</brief_title>
  <official_title>To Investigate the Effect of Early Community-care Program on Physical and Depressive Aspects for Discharged Hospital Patient Suffered From Hip Fracture.</official_title>
